OL,3,CAmmanford school where teachers and
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed to reopen tomorrow
OL,6,FThe school in Carmarthenshire where
OL,7,Ftwo teachers and a teenager were
OL,8,Fstabbed on Wednesday will reopen its
OL,9,Fdoors to pupils tomorrow for the first
OL,10,Ftime since the incident which shocked
OL,11,Fthe community.
OL,13,FEducation and child psychology
OL,14,Fspecialists will be at Ysgol Dyffryn
OL,15,FAman in Ammanford for two weeks
OL,16,Fsupporting pupils and staff, following
OL,17,Fthe attack that left teachers Fiona
OL,18,FElias, Liz Hopkins and a teenager
OL,19,Finjured.
