OL,6,FA 13 year old girl, who cannot be
OL,7,Fnamed due to her age, was charged with
OL,8,Fthree counts of attempted murder and
OL,9,Fis on remand at secure youth detention
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FShe is due to appear at Swansea Crown
OL,13,FCourt on May 27th.
OL,15,FIn a letter posted on social media,
OL,16,Fthe school said: "I hope that this
OL,17,Fmessage finds you and your children
OL,18,Fwell.
