OL,6,F"Thank you to our staff who have been
OL,7,Fworking hard to ensure that the school
OL,8,Fwill be ready to be re-opened to
OL,9,Fpupils on Monday, 29 April.
OL,11,F"A broad range of wellbeing support
OL,12,Fwill continue to be offered to all
OL,13,Fpupils, teachers and staff at Dyffryn
OL,14,FAman when we re-open.
OL,16,F"In collaboration with the County
OL,17,FCouncil, we have set out a wellbeing
OL,18,Fsupport plan to help all pupils and
OL,19,Fstaff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
