OL,6,F"A dedicated Education and Child
OL,7,FPsychology Team from the Council will
OL,8,Fbe available for pupils and staff to
OL,9,Faccess. This team will maintain a
OL,10,Fpresence at the school for the next
OL,11,Ftwo weeks to provide ongoing support
OL,12,Fand assistance as needed.
OL,14,F"Counselling will be available for
OL,15,Fsupport and guidance to all students
OL,16,Ffacing difficulties. The school and
OL,17,Fthe local authority have also received
OL,18,Fnumerous offers of support from
OL,19,Fexternal agencies to provide
OL,20,Fadditional assistance for our students
OL,21,Fduring this time.
