OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F463A1714330237
OL,3,CAmmanford school where teachers and
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed to reopen tomorrow
OL,6,F"Together with the Council, we are
OL,7,Fcarefully considering how and when to
OL,8,Fuse these services. This week will
OL,9,Fstay in our minds for a long time to
OL,10,Fcome.
OL,12,F"I am so very proud of our school
OL,13,Fcommunity for the way we have pulled
OL,14,Ftogether. My thanks go to everyone who
OL,15,Fhas shown their support to the school,
OL,16,Fin various ways, to aid our
OL,17,Fpreparation to be able to re-open
OL,18,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman to pupils, teachers
OL,19,Fand staff on Monday."
