OL,6,FIt comes after Chief Constable of
OL,7,FDyfed Powys Police, Richard Lewis,
OL,8,Fpraised staff, pupils, and "the wider
OL,9,Fschool family" for their impressive
OL,10,Fresponse to the incident at Ysgol
OL,11,FDyffryn Aman.
OL,13,FHe said: "There remains a live
OL,14,Finvestigation and whilst we must of
OL,15,Fcourse be careful not to compromise
OL,16,Fthis work, early indications show that
OL,17,Fthe immediate response of your staff
OL,18,Fand pupils is deserving of significant
OL,19,Fpraise.
