OL,4,Cteenager stabbed to reopen tomorrow
OL,6,F"I'm aware that some pupils and staff
OL,7,Fwere more immediately involved than
OL,8,Fothers and I'm sure there will be an
OL,9,Fappropriate time in the future to
OL,10,Fofficially recognise the role they
OL,11,Fplayed in bringing the incident to a
OL,12,Fclose.
OL,14,F"My praise also extends to the
OL,15,Ffamilies of pupils and staff who
OL,16,Fattend the school and the calm and
OL,17,Fmeasured way that they patiently
OL,18,Fwaited for news following the
OL,19,Fincident. The response was a real
OL,20,F'whole community' effort in the best
OL,21,Ftraditions of west Wales."
